{"title":"江海行（二首）","authors":["元辉"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"江海行（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月乘船下珠江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月乘船下珠江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一程水浪一程香："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧不够丛丛橘树笼红云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不断夹岸香蕉串串黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土肥杨桃枝头密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树高木瓜串儿长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔗林漫长堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沃野凝蜜糖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦色入南海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采歌百里扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问船工：鲜果运何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国品评北国尝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠江一条输香带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜情蜜意流四方！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打蠔谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽袖试蠔刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷裤看退潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一叶滑板泥滩上漂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边去打蠔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮平海滩阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满地露蠔帽："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密鳞蠔、僧帽蠔、瓦刺蠔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里蠔场凝脂膏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬至蠔肉肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路油渍漂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫等潮回水遮路啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快呀快打捞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这滩忙打蠔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那滩育蠔苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水不枯石不烂啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日赶海潮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蠔篓沉甸甸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声一串串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声化入千家灶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉盘盛珍肴……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}